\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 1.\tab}}\pard\plain \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
He that dwelleth in the help of the Most High shall abide in the shelter of the God of heaven. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 2.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
He shall say unto the Lord: Thou art my helper and my refuge. He is my God, and I will hope in Him. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 3.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
