\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 4.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
With His shoulders will He overshadow thee, and under His wings shalt thou have hope. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 5.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
With a shield will His truth encompass thee; thou shalt not be afraid for the terror by night, nor for the arrow that flieth by day, 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 6.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
Nor for the thing that walketh in darkness, nor for the mishap and demon of noonday. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 7.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
A thousand shall fall at thy side, and ten thousand at thy right hand, but unto thee shall it not come nigh. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 8.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
Only with thine eyes shalt thou behold, and thou shalt see the reward of sinners. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 9.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
For Thou, O Lord, art my hope. Thou madest the Most High thy refuge; 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 10.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
No evils shall come nigh thee, and no scourge shall draw nigh unto thy dwelling. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 11.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
For He shall give His angels charge over thee, to keep thee in all thy ways. 
\par }\pard \qj\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlcont\ilvl0\ls0\pnrnot0\pndec }\adjustright {\fs28 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 12.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
On their hands shall they bear thee up, lest at any time thou dash thy foot against a stone. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 13.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
Upon the asp and basilisk shalt thou tread, and thou shalt trample upon the lion and dragon. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 14.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
For he hath set his hope on Me, and I will deliver him; I will shelter him because he hath known My name. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 15.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 
He shall cry unto Me, and I will hearken unto him. I am with him in affliction, and I will rescue him and glorify him. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 16.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls1\adjustright {\fs28 With 
length of days will I satisfy him, and I will show him My salvation. 
