Blessed are the blameless in the way, who walk in the law of the Lord. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 2.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Blessed are they that search out His testimonies; with their whole heart shall they seek after Him. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 3.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
