\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 65.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Thou hast dealt graciously with Thy servant, O Lord, according to Thy word. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 66.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Goodness and discipline and knowledge teach Thou me, for in Thy commandments have I believed. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 67.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Before I was humbled, I transgressed; therefore Thy saying have I kept. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 68.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 Thou ar
t good, O Lord, and in Thy goodness teach me Thy statutes. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 69.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Multiplied against me hath been the unrighteousness of the proud; but as for me, with my whole heart will I search out Thy commandments. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 70.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Curdled like milk is their heart; but as for me, in Thy law have I meditated. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 71.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
It is good for me that Thou hast humbled me, that I might learn Thy statutes. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 72.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
The law of Thy mouth is better to me than thousands of gold and silver. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 73.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Thy hands have made me and fashioned me; give me understanding and I will learn Thy commandments. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 74.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
They that fear Thee shall see me and be glad, for on Thy words have I set my hope. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 75.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
I have known, O Lord, that Thy judgements are righteousness, and with truth hast Thou humbled me. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 76.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Let now Thy mercy be my comfort, according to Thy saying unto Thy servant. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 77.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Let Thy compassions come upon me and I shall live, for Thy law is my meditation. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 78.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Let the proud be put to shame, for unjustly have they transgressed against me; but as for me, I will ponder on Thy commandments. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 79.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 Let those that fear Thee 
return unto me, and those that know Thy testimonies. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 80.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Let my heart be blameless in Thy statutes, that I may not be put to shame. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 81.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
My soul fainteth for Thy salvation; on Thy words have I set my hope. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 82.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Mine eyes are grown dim with waiting for Thine oracle; they say: When wilt Thou comfort me? 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 83.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
For I am become like a wine-skin in the frost; yet Thy statutes have I not forgotten. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 84.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
How many are the days of Thy servant? When wilt Thou execute judgement for me on them that persecute me? 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 85.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 Transgressors have told me
 fables, but they are not like Thy law, O Lord. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 86.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
All Thy commandments are truth. Without a cause have men persecuted me; do Thou help me. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 87.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
They well nigh made an end of me on the earth; but as for me, I forsook not Thy commandments. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 88.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 According to Thy mercy
 quicken me, and I will keep the testimonies of Thy mouth. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 89.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
For ever, O Lord, Thy word abideth in heaven. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 90.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Unto generation and generation is Thy truth; Thou hast laid the foundation of the earth, and it abideth. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 91.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
By Thine ordinance doth the day abide, for all things are Thy servants. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 92.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
If Thy law had not been my meditation, then should I have perished in my humiliation. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 93.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
I will never forget Thy statutes, for in them hast Thou quickened me. 
