\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 147.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
I arose in the dead of night and I cried; on Thy words have I set my hope. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 148.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Mine eyes woke before the morning that I might meditate on Thy sayings. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 149.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Hear my voice, O Lord, according to Thy mercy; according to Thy judgement, quicken me. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 150.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
They have drawn nigh that lawlessly persecute me, but from Thy law are they far removed. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 151.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Near art Thou, O Lord, and all Thy ways are truth. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 152.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
From the beginning I have known from Thy testimonies that Thou hast founded them for ever. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 153.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 Behold my humiliat
ion and rescue me, for Thy law have I not forgotten. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 154.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Judge my cause and redeem me; for Thy word's sake quicken me. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 155.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Far from sinners is salvation, for they have not sought after Thy statutes. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 156.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Thy compassions are many, O Lord; according to Thy judgement quicken me. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 157.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Many are they that persecute me and afflict me; from Thy testimonies have I not declined. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 158.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
I beheld men acting foolishly and I pined away, because they kept not Thy sayings. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 159.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Behold, how I have loved Thy commandments; O Lord, in Thy mercy, quicken me. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 160.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
The beginning of Thy words is truth, and all the judgements of Thy righteousness endure for ever. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 161.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Princes have persecuted me without a cause, and because of Thy words my heart hath been afraid. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 162.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
I will rejoice in Thy sayings as one that findeth great spoil. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 163.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Unrighteousness have I hated and abhorred, but Thy law have I loved. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 164.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Seven times a day have I praised Thee for the judgements of Thy righteousness. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 165.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Much peace have they that love Thy law, and for them there is no stumbling-block. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 166.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 I awaited 
Thy salvation, O Lord, and Thy commandments have I loved. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 167.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
My soul hath kept Thy testimonies and hath loved them exceedingly. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 168.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
I have kept Thy commandments and Thy testimonies, for all my ways are before Thee, O Lord. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 169.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Let my supplication draw nigh before Thee, O Lord; according to Thine oracle give me understanding. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 170.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Let my petition come before Thee, O Lord; according to Thine oracle deliver me. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 171.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
My lips shall pour forth a hymn when Thou hast taught me Thy statutes. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 172.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
My tongue shall speak of Thy sayings, for all Thy commandments are righteousness. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 173.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
Let Thy hand be for saving me, for I have chosen Thy commandments. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 174.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
I have longed for Thy salvation, O Lord, and Thy law is my meditation. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 175.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
My soul shall live and shall praise Thee, and Thy judgements will help me. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs28 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 176.\tab}}\pard \qj\fi-360\li360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls2\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\ls2\adjustright {\fs28 
I have gone astray like a sheep that is lost; O seek Thy servant, for I have not forgotten Thy commandments. 
